All right, let's let the dust&nbsp;settle, take a deep breath, and process everything&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:31.840 --> 00:09:39.840
we just witnessed. A few quick clarifications are&nbsp;
in order. First of all, Veo 4 Omni is the only model&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:46.640
in this shootout limited strictly to 10 seconds&nbsp;
